    <item>
      <title>火箭实验室将中子火箭首次飞行推迟至 2025 年中期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/rocket-lab-delays-first-flight-of-neutron-rocket-to-mid-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rocket Lab USA Inc. 将其大型中子火箭的首次发射最早推迟了几个月，推迟到 2025 年中期，因为这家小型卫星发射公司正在开发发动机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/rocket-lab-delays-first-flight-of-neutron-rocket-to-mid-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 22:53:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MercadoLibre 的金融科技部门被银行指控“滥用行为”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/banks-accuse-mercadolibre-s-fintech-arm-of-abusive-conduct</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷银行周一对 MercadoLibre Inc. 提起法律诉讼，指控其在数字支付平台上存在“滥用行为”，在央行新法规对金融科技行业实施重大变革后，该公司面临的压力加大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/banks-accuse-mercadolibre-s-fintech-arm-of-abusive-conduct</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 22:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
